<del rend="strikethrough">Suntag nach ſant <expan>Margrete<ex>n</ex></expan> tag hie ſein ſol vor </del> <expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_83_r1l46">cʒwen tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_83_line_1576658908179_5288">vor <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> lanfride </ab><ab facs="#facs_83_line_1576658910867_5293">der nu ſchierſt </ab><ab facs="#facs_83_line_1576658914425_5298">hie ſein wirdt </ab></add> her 
