</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_83" id="40r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan> und
